<h2>Thank you!</h2>

<h3>Hi there <%= @voucher.user.email %> </h3>

<p>
We have sent you a discount voucher to use at <%= @voucher.deal.title %>. 
Below are the voucher details. Please show them the QR code and you can get discount!
</p>

<div>
    <strong>Title:</strong>
    <p><%= @voucher.deal.title %></p>
    <strong>Address:</strong>
    <p><%= @voucher.deal.merchant.full_address %></p>
    <strong>Voucher price:</strong>
    <p><%= @voucher.deal.offer_price %></p>
    <strong>Expiry:</strong>
    <p><%= @voucher.deal.expiry %></p>
    <strong>QRcode:</strong>
    <%= image_tag @voucher.qrcode_url %>
</div>
<br>
<br>

Enjoy!

Nowcher team